---
title: Karahi-Inspired Curry Tofu with Golden Tomato-Pepper Gravy and Spinach Rice
description: This recipe of tofu simmered in a  gentle tomato curry broth is inspired by the flavors of karahi curries. It gets amped up by the bright, tangy and unexpected hit of roasted red pepper pesto.
